{
  "frontCover": "Front cover of a birthday greeting card in a 9:16 ratio, featuring a dreamy fantasy anime style. The artwork depicts two stylized, cartoon-illustrated characters riding on the back of a fluffy, moth-like creature with large, expressive blue eyes and feathery antennae. The character on the left has curly black hair, a dark patterned shirt, and is winking with a wide, joyful smile. The character on the right wears a light-colored hijab and a warm red sweater, also smiling broadly. They are both joyfully interacting, conveying a sense of fun and camaraderie. The background is a magical, twilight sky filled with soft purple, pink, and orange hues, suggesting a fantastical journey. Scattered throughout the sky are translucent, glowing jellyfish. In the foreground, oversized, whimsical mushrooms with glowing caps in shades of orange and blue, alongside sparkling crystals, create an enchanted landscape. The color palette is dominated by soft pastels and vibrant, magical tones. The text \"Happy Birthday Sunny\" is written in a flowing, elegant, handwritten cursive script in a light, creamy color, positioned centrally and clearly readable, avoiding the top and bottom 10% of the image. The overall mood is quirky, unique, and enchanting, with a full-bleed background extending to the edges.",
  "backCover": "Back cover of a birthday greeting card in a 9:16 ratio, continuing the dreamy fantasy anime style. The design is simple, serene, and subtly creative, featuring elements that echo the front cover without being explicit. The background is a continuation of the magical twilight sky with soft pastel gradients of purple and pink, and a few faint, glowing jellyfish scattered at a distance. In the lower left portion of the card, a stylized, glowing mushroom with a soft orange cap is visible. Towards the center-left, a cluster of sparkling, translucent crystals in soft blues and purples adds a touch of enchantment. The bottom-right corner (approximately 1 inch square) is left completely clear and undecorated for a QR code. The overall mood is peaceful and complementary to the front and interior pages, with a full-bleed background extending to the edges.",
  "leftInterior": "Left interior page of a birthday greeting card in a 9:16 ratio, in a dreamy fantasy anime style. This page is an artistic playground, showcasing a whimsical, unique, and unexpected scene that complements the front cover's theme. The background is a continuation of the magical twilight sky, but here it transforms into a swirling nebula of cosmic dust and distant galaxies in soft purples, blues, and pinks. Floating amidst this cosmic expanse are abstract, glowing shapes and patterns that suggest celestial phenomena. There are no people on this page. The overall mood is enchanting and vast, evoking a sense of wonder and adventure. The artwork should be a bold, imaginative artistic choice that feels like part of the same artistic universe, with soft pastels, magical atmosphere, and detailed nature elements integrated in an abstract, whimsical manner. Full-bleed background extending to the edges.",
  "rightInterior": "Right interior page of a birthday greeting card in a 9:16 ratio, in a dreamy fantasy anime style. This page features the message text: \"Sunny, another year of orbiting the sun together and you're still my favorite weirdo in the entire galaxy. They say wisdom comes with age, but I'm glad we've just gotten better at being ridiculous. Here's to another trip around the big fiery star, my friend. Happy Birthday from your partner-in-shenanigans, Rana\". The text is written in a beautiful, clearly readable handwritten cursive script with a pen-style appearance, featuring natural ink flow and slight variations in line weight, conveying warmth and genuine emotion. The handwriting is elegant and personal, not overly perfect but graceful. The message is integrated into innovative decorative artwork that frames it without being clichÃ©. The artwork includes elements from the front cover, such as stylized, glowing mushrooms with soft orange and blue caps, and sparkling crystals in blues and purples, all set against a background of the magical twilight sky with subtle nebulae and faint, distant glowing jellyfish. The decorative elements are artistic and unconventional, enhancing the message and the overall quirky, unique, and enchanting tone. The composition is designed to be visually harmonious with the left interior page, creating a cohesive spread. The text is positioned safely in the center area, avoiding the top and bottom 10% of the image, with a full-bleed background extending to the edges."
}
